  "text": {
    "en": {
      "name": "Shopina the Melodious Maestra",
      "official": false
    },
    "de": {
      "name": "Shopina die musikalische Maestra",
      "effect": "Einmal pro Spielzug: Du kannst 1 LICHT Monster vom Typ Fee in deinem Friedhof w\u00e4hlen; f\u00fcge es deiner Hand hinzu. Du kannst w\u00e4hrend des Spielzugs, in dem du diesen Effekt aktivierst, keine Effekte von Nicht-LICHT Monstern aktivieren."
    },
    "es": {
      "name": "Chopina la Maestra Melodiosa",
      "effect": "Una vez por turno: puedes seleccionar 1 monstruo de LUZ de Tipo Hada en tu Cementerio; a\u00f1\u00e1delo a tu mano. Durante el turno en el que activas este efecto, no puedes activar efectos de monstruos que no sean de LUZ."
    },
    "fr": {
      "name": "Shopina la Maestria de la Musique",
      "effect": "Une fois par tour : vous pouvez cibler 1 monstre LUMI\u00c8RE de Type Elfe dans votre Cimeti\u00e8re ; ajoutez-le \u00e0 votre main. Vous ne pouvez pas activer des effets de monstre non-LUMI\u00c8RE durant le tour o\u00f9 vous activez cet effet."
    },
    "it": {
      "name": "Shopina la Maestra Melodiosa",
      "effect": "Una volta per turno: puoi scegliere come bersaglio 1 mostro LUCE di Tipo Fata nel tuo Cimitero; aggiungilo alla tua mano. Non puoi attivare effetti di mostri non-LUCE durante il turno in cui attivi questo effetto."
    },
    "pt": {
      "name": "Shopina, a Diva Melodiosa",
      "effect": "Uma vez por turno: voc\u00ea pode escolher 1 monstro de LUZ do Tipo Fada no seu Cemit\u00e9rio; adicione-o \u00e0 sua m\u00e3o. Voc\u00ea n\u00e3o pode ativar os efeitos de monstros que n\u00e3o forem de LUZ durante o turno em que ativar este efeito."
    },
    "ja": {
      "name": "\u5e7b\u594f\u306e\u97f3\u59eb\u30ed\u30fc\u30ea\u30a4\u30c3\u30c8\u30fb\u30d5\u30e9\u30f3\u30bd\u30ef",
      "effect": "\u3053\u306e\u30ab\u30fc\u30c9\u306e\u52b9\u679c\u3092\u767a\u52d5\u3059\u308b\u30bf\u30fc\u30f3\u3001\u81ea\u5206\u306f\u5149\u5c5e\u6027\u4ee5\u5916\u306e\u30e2\u30f3\u30b9\u30bf\u30fc\u306e\u52b9\u679c\u3092\u767a\u52d5\u3067\u304d\u306a\u3044\u3002\u2460\uff1a\uff11\u30bf\u30fc\u30f3\u306b\uff11\u5ea6\u3001\u81ea\u5206\u306e\u5893\u5730\u306e\u5929\u4f7f\u65cf\u30fb\u5149\u5c5e\u6027\u30e2\u30f3\u30b9\u30bf\u30fc\uff11\u4f53\u3092\u5bfe\u8c61\u3068\u3057\u3066\u767a\u52d5\u3067\u304d\u308b\u3002\u305d\u306e\u30e2\u30f3\u30b9\u30bf\u30fc\u3092\u624b\u672d\u306b\u52a0\u3048\u308b\u3002"
    },
    "ko": {
